<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFAE6A11FD209A0B1B03B6B5" pageId="85" pageNumber="843" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFAE6A11FD209A0B1B03B6B5" blockId="85.[731,1325,3039,3463]" pageId="85" pageNumber="843">
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAE6A11FD209A0B1D4EB741" box="[732,846,3154,3187]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Eptesicus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="85" pageNumber="843" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Eptesicus</taxonomicName>
as currently defined is paraphyletic with respect to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAE6A11FC299AD81A47B7A8" box="[981,1095,3201,3226]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="85" pageNumber="843" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Histiotus</taxonomicName>
, which is closely related to the New World 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAE6A11FBC69AF81AAEB7F0" box="[1082,1198,3233,3266]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Eptesicus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="85" pageNumber="843" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Eptesicus</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAE6A11FB479AF81B2DB7F0" box="[1211,1325,3233,3266]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="85" pageNumber="843" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Histiotus</taxonomicName>
is recognized as a distinct genus here based on its morphological distinctions, and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAE6A11FB089AA91D2CB60A" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Eptesicus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="85" pageNumber="843" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Eptesicus</taxonomicName>
will likely be split into multiple genera in the near future to avoid paraphyly. Eleven subspecies currently recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
